## ConsoleCompiler (Tech-Printer) Localization — EN-US

# Console Compiler entity
ent-NCConsoleCompiler = Console Compiler
    .desc = A high-tech data terminal that converts digital codes into physical blueprints and recipes. Feed it raw data and insert decrypted technology disks to print.

# Raw Data tiers
ent-NCRawDataT1 = Raw Data (Tier 1)
    .desc = A low-grade data shard. Worth 100 data points when digitized.

ent-NCRawDataT2 = Raw Data (Tier 2)
    .desc = A mid-grade data shard. Worth 300 data points when digitized.

ent-NCRawDataT3 = Raw Data (Tier 3)
    .desc = A high-grade data shard. Worth 500 data points when digitized.

# Burned disk
ent-NCRawDataBurned = Burned Disk
    .desc = A spent and burned data disk. Completely useless.
